</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[182,1137,291,324]" pageId="104" pageNumber="383" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="104.[181,1390,291,604]" box="[182,1137,291,324]" pageId="104" pageNumber="383">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[182,417,291,324]" pageId="104" pageNumber="383">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
The Oldfield Deermouse is presumably nocturnal.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[183,1123,330,363]" pageId="104" pageNumber="383" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph blockId="104.[181,1390,291,604]" box="[183,1123,330,363]" pageId="104" pageNumber="383">
